answers.body_markdown:
Your IDE cannot autocomplete &quot;Connection&quot; because you didn&#39;t import the `Connection` class to your JSP file.

You need to add an import statement for `Connection` like so:

    &lt;%@page import=&quot;java.sql.Connection&quot;%&gt;

Alternatively, you can be a bit lazy and just import the entire `java.sql` package:

    &lt;%@page import=&quot;java.sql.*&quot;%&gt;

Once you set up your file properly, your IDE should be able to autocomplete properly.

